title: Biden's Coronavirus Malaise
description: Fellas discuss Biden's decline, Kamala's actors and the Southwest debacle before playing a game of Dem or Journo. U.S. Senate candidate, Carla Sands, joins the progrum to talk about her race for the Republican nomination in Pennsylvania.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Carla Sands, Comfortably Smug, Josh Holmes, Michael Duncan)
